# Build artifacts
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/out
**/build
**/.turbo

# Test / coverage
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Editor / OS
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp

# Git / GitHub
.git
.gitignore
.github

# Env / secrets — provided via Render env vars at runtime, NEVER bake into image
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Vercel — not used by Docker target
.vercel
**/.vercel

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*

# Claude / agent
.claude
CLAUDE.md
.impeccable.md

# Project deliverables / docs not needed at runtime
SUBMISSION.md
DEPLOY.md
README.md

# Finder duplicates (just in case any sneak back)
**/* 2.*
**/* 3.*
